BTTTriggerConfig.BTTTouchBarAppleScriptString: set json to do shell script "curl -H 'CB-VERSION: 2015-04-08' https://api.coinbase.com/v2/prices/BTC-USD/spot"set json to do shell script "sed s/warnings.*//g <<< " & jsonset value to do shell script "sed s/[a-zA-Z:{},]//g <<< " & jsonset btc to do shell script "sed s/[.]/,/g <<< " & valueset pay to do shell script "curl -s 'https://bittrex.com/api/v1.1/public/getticker?market=btc-xmr' | grep -oE '(Last).*' | sed 's/[^0-9\\.]*//g' | tr . ,"set pay to do shell script "sed s/[.]/,/g <<< " & payset pay to pay as realset answer to pay * btcset answer to answer * 100set answer to round answerset answer to answer / 100return "$" & answer
